{
  "message": "test(fuzz): add 36 datetime_parsing corpus seeds\n\nCovers datetime and timedelta parsing edge cases:\n- ISO 8601 dates: basic, with time, microseconds, UTC, timezones\n- Epoch and boundary dates: 1970-01-01, min/max datetime\n- Leap year handling: 2000-02-29, 2100-02-28\n- Timedelta formats: day/days/hour/minutes/seconds/ms/us/ns\n- Combined timedeltas: \"1 day 2 hours 30 minutes\"\n- Negative timedeltas\n- ISO 8601 durations: P1Y2M3DT4H5M6S, PT1H30M\n- Format variants: week dates, ordinal dates, space separator\n- Edge cases: empty, whitespace, NaT\n- Multi-line inputs for array parsing\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
